Order! Order in this courtroom. Order!

954
01:00:16,879 --> 01:00:18,348
(GAVEL BANGING)

955
01:00:18,381 --> 01:00:20,183
Order in this court!

956
01:00:22,385 --> 01:00:23,720
What are you doing?

957
01:00:23,753 --> 01:00:25,688
Lady! You sit down!

958
01:00:27,023 --> 01:00:28,725
JUDGE: Order in this courtroom, please.

959
01:00:31,894 --> 01:00:34,864
I see that there are cameras in the courtroom.

960
01:00:34,897 --> 01:00:38,101
People taking notes, writing books.

961
01:00:39,736 --> 01:00:42,605
But I will not tolerate these outbursts!

962
01:00:43,773 --> 01:00:45,508
All right?

963
01:00:45,541 --> 01:00:48,678
Now, we've heard some eloquent words by our District Attorney.

964
01:00:48,711 --> 01:00:53,016
Now I'm sure we will hear more eloquent words from our counsel for the defense.

965
01:00:53,750 --> 01:00:54,751
Counselor.

966
01:00:57,954 --> 01:01:00,423
(PEOPLE MURMURING)

967
01:01:04,193 --> 01:01:06,462
Ladies and gentlemen of the jury.

968
01:01:07,630 --> 01:01:11,034
To say these are unusual charges

969
01:01:11,067 --> 01:01:13,569
is an understatement of the worst order.

970
01:01:13,603 --> 01:01:16,906
These are impossible charges.

971
01:01:16,939 --> 01:01:20,510
I assure you that our defense will rest on the fact

972
01:01:20,543 --> 01:01:23,713
that this case is not about abortion.

973
01:01:23,746 --> 01:01:27,884
This case is about a simple attempted suicide.

974
01:01:27,917 --> 01:01:34,190
Let me tell you the real story of what happened one hot summer night in August.

975
01:01:34,223 --> 01:01:38,127
Jed Jackson staggered home drunk and woke his wife from a sound sleep.

976
01:01:38,161 --> 01:01:40,530
He picked a fight and lost control.

977
01:01:40,563 --> 01:01:43,900
I assure you that Jed Jackson

978
01:01:43,933 --> 01:01:48,838
will not deny the fact that he beat his wife until her face was black and blue!

979
01:01:50,339 --> 01:01:55,244
My client, physically and emotionally abused,

980
01:01:55,278 --> 01:01:59,415
susceptible to depression and impulsive behavior, chose suicide.

981
01:02:01,017 --> 01:02:04,454
How can the state charge Bonnie Jackson with criminal abortion

982
01:02:04,487 --> 01:02:06,189
when she did not know she was pregnant?

983
01:02:09,125 --> 01:02:12,395
Where is the intent?

984
01:02:12,428 --> 01:02:18,601
How could she notify her spouse of something she had no knowledge of?

985
01:02:18,634 --> 01:02:25,141
How could she have interfered with her husband's so-called property rights?

986
01:02:25,174 --> 01:02:31,080
I ask you, is any one person the property of another?

987
01:02:31,114 --> 01:02:34,450
These are innocent babies! Young woman, you need to settle down.

988
01:02:34,484 --> 01:02:35,885
(ALL SHOUTING)

989
01:02:37,620 --> 01:02:38,921
Stop this.

990
01:02:38,955 --> 01:02:40,723
You sit down, lady.

991
01:02:42,792 --> 01:02:46,095
Finally, to the question regarding a husband's right

992
01:02:46,129 --> 01:02:49,432
in the decision of when to end a pregnancy,

993
01:02:49,465 --> 01:02:54,137
I can only reply that this issue has no place here.

994
01:02:54,170 --> 01:02:56,806
This is all bullshit! Why don't you go back to New York.

995
01:02:58,908 --> 01:03:00,843
(GAVEL BANGING)

996
01:03:00,877 --> 01:03:05,548
The reason that Bonnie Jackson stands here accused today is because she is a woman.

997
01:03:05,581 --> 01:03:08,284
(PEOPLE CLAMORING)

998
01:03:08,317 --> 01:03:12,021
And on that count, we plead for freedom!

999
01:03:15,391 --> 01:03:17,560
JUDGE: Order! Please be seated!

1000
01:03:17,593 --> 01:03:20,696
Bravo! Bravo!

1001
01:03:22,665 --> 01:03:24,333
(PEOPLE WHISTLING)

1002
01:03:24,367 --> 01:03:26,903
Stop this applause! Stop this!

1003
01:03:26,936 --> 01:03:28,771
This is not a rock concert!

1004
01:03:30,573 --> 01:03:33,209
The decision for a woman to have a child

1005
01:03:33,242 --> 01:03:36,979
may be one of the most important decisions she ever makes.

1006
01:03:37,013 --> 01:03:39,882
(ALL ARGUING)

1007
01:03:39,916 --> 01:03:41,517
Your Honor, will you do something?

1008
01:03:41,551 --> 01:03:42,919
Stop it!

1009
01:03:42,952 --> 01:03:46,522
You take away that decision, and you take away her dignity.

1010
01:03:46,556 --> 01:03:48,591
MAN: Get her out of this courtroom.

1011
01:03:49,792 --> 01:03:51,727
I saved this child's life!

1012
01:03:51,761 --> 01:03:53,930
I saved this child's life!

1013
01:03:53,963 --> 01:03:55,698
This could have been an unborn child, but I saved her.

1014
01:03:55,731 --> 01:03:56,732
Stop this!

1015
01:04:00,436 --> 01:04:04,073
Court will resume at 10:00 in the morning.

1016
01:04:04,106 --> 01:04:05,875
This court is adjourned.

